{"tid":1547441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美領之鬼","createTime":"2019-09-06T16:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T16:20:28.000Z","uid":226344,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"07ab47a7beace4f2360fdfeac2eed33967f7cbee","tid":1547441,"uid":226344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:11:50.000Z","msg":"出黎啦,鬼,我地好驚你架,夠膽就搞美領<br />\n<br />\n我地手足係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">絕對唔會</span></span>搞美領          <br />\n我地手足係絕對唔會<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">搞</span></span>美領<br />\n我地手足係絕對唔會搞<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">美領</span></span><br />\n<br />\n聽講做臥底既人都有個覺悟,就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">身首</span><span style=\"color: maroon;\">異處</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果大家見到鬼,唔好再心軟,你望下幾多手足受左幾大既傷害,你仲要做何式凝?<br />\n<br />\n唔好畀佢地走得甩,首要係保護自己既同時一直跑,再先擊跨佢<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">逃走用既雙腳</span></span><br />\n唔好畀佢地走得甩,首要係保護自己既同時一直跑,再先擊跨佢<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">逃走用既雙腳</span></span><br />\n唔好畀佢地走得甩,首要係保護自己既同時一直跑,再先擊跨佢<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">逃走用既雙腳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">鬼</span>    我好撚驚啊,我好撚驚你唔做野啊<br />\n<br />\n係啊,講緊你啊"},{"pid":"5374bf9f28d9fbd8d03dac5ca92d9d944a3200eb","tid":1547441,"uid":226344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:18:08.000Z","msg":"屌晒你地班何式撚"},{"pid":"b7eb1e92ee41f1775c03fa8bb16bb817bd85572f","tid":1547441,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:20:28.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?